                            GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
                        </a>.<br />
                        <small>
                            If you modify and use this over a network, you must make the modified source available to users.
                        </small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="text-muted">
                        <strong>Links:</strong><br />
                        <a href="https://github.com/nwtobbe/BareProx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
